---
title: Honey Yogurt & Waffle Parfaits with Berry Compote, Toasted Cashews & Coconut
description: This wholesome quickie breakfast idea has layers and layers of delicious flavors and textures. It starts with creamy, tangy honey yogurt that’s topped with our sweet berry compote, then crunchy toasted cashews and coconut, and fluffy toasted Belgian waffle pieces. Serve it in a glass container for the full parfait effect. This satisfying crowd pleaser all comes together in just 15 minutes leaving you with lots of extra morning time we’re sure you’ll make good use of—absolutely par-fect!
